      "content": "i'm just worried about being super dramatic about it lol. i mean, it's just wine, not like whiskey or something. if i just have a half glass or maybe a little bit of white wine, it's way lighter than red wine right? i really don't want to miss out on the toast. are you absolutely sure it's dangerous? feels like a lot of hassle for just a tiny bit of wine.",
